Gary Crosby (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gary_Crosby_(actor) 0 Gary Evan Crosby (June 27, 1933 – August 24, 1995) was an American singer and actor. His parents were Bing Crosby, of whom he wrote a highly critical memoir, and the singer and actress Dixie Lee.
